ComicInfo.Title: The Manchu of C'nal Street, Part 1: The Challenge of Chang; The Manchu of C'nal Street, Part 2: Death before Dishonor
ComicInfo.Summary:
The Manchu of C'nal Street, Part 1: The Challenge of Chang: Samson encounters another mighty warrior in what had been Chinatown, but learns that Terra of Jerz rules there.
The Manchu of C'nal Street, Part 2: Death before Dishonor: Terra forces Chang and Samson to fight each other, but they form an alliance, drive Terra from her throne, and replace her with Chang.
